  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13099567/getting-to-resort-hero.jpg" alt="resorthero" data-udi="umb://media/3796c46da47e419d9947b522df5cbe3d" /></p>
<p><strong>Reaching your resort:</strong></p>
<p><strong>Train</strong> - with resorts across many European destinations reachable by train, travelling to your ski holiday this way is relaxing, easy and offers plenty of room for your legs and also your luggage. Offering a multitude of train journeys to our customers is also a part of our vision for the future, a more planet friendly way of travel. </p>
<p><strong>Plane</strong> - flying from airports across the whole of the UK, we are sure that you will be able to find a plane journey that works best for your ski holiday. Not only to destinations across Europe but also <a data-udi="umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3}" title="Canada">Canada</a>, including some of their world-famous resorts. </p>
<p><strong>Car</strong> - this can be the prefect option for any ski holiday when wanting to travel at your own pace, take additional luggage or create your own journey that suits travelling with small children. With many our our resorts reachable by car and offering on-site parking at accommodation, it is a great option. </p>
<p><em>Booking your next ski trip? Keep up to date on Inghams ski holidays on our <a data-udi="umb://document/4323a332132044fba8041dc874c3bc85" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4323a332132044fba8041dc874c3bc85}" title="What's new on the slopes">What's new on the slopes page</a> for all the latest on new resorts, offers, accommodation, travel and more. </em></p>]]></bodyText>
